{"tid":944602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微信上稱「豬肉不能吃」 陸女遭警方拘留","createTime":"2018-12-17T09:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T09:42:18.000Z","uid":75969,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"09d78776a89725d6eeefa752876738385b4541ac","tid":944602,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/12/17/realtime/5672861.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F12%2F17%2Frealtime%2F5672861.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=8e588f53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天津武清一名女子在微信朋友圈發布「豬肉不能吃」的消息，被指散布謠言，遭當地警方行政拘留。<br />\n<br />\n澎湃新聞引述天津武清警方消息稱，近日，武清部分微信群和朋友圈中開始傳播一則消息，內容是「告訴大家一個重要通知：昨天我的一個朋友她姑爺在技術監督局上班、最近幾天在武清各大超市已經查出細菌豬肉流入市場、還有火腿腸、尤其是雙匯的，你們千萬不要再吃豬肉了最近，消息非常可靠、其他牛肉、羊肉、雞肉可以吃，切記！」這則消息被大量轉發，引起天津武清警方高度重視。<br />\n<br />\n經當地警方調查，該則消息傳播人是武清區居民劉姓女子。12月14日，警方將劉姓女子傳喚到派出所，並以虛構事實擾亂公共秩序，對她處以行政拘留，整起案件正進一步審理中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7332/3541485\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7332%2F3541485&d=38KyZA03mmW%2Bd8urcvfUcUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=bee3ca19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7332/3541485</a><br />\n<br />\n入去坐日日俾豬肉你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893ef9b5490f3e1db2e1dfbce71e76d39744bba6","tid":944602,"uid":218385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:15:03.000Z","msg":"因為太誠實 被人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a381e7c54bc4db5af07205070ad4afc88feb5d9d","tid":944602,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:16:04.000Z","msg":"官方證實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa95cdfa4e41a4c5ac7256fc7bfe8ba97177d8a","tid":944602,"uid":17765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:17:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3mYNAB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3mYNAB.png&h=775cbf60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n驚閪咩"},{"pid":"027ca441f4bd5d82dcaa9f772df5f560fbc08394","tid":944602,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:22:40.000Z","msg":"我的一個朋友她姑爺在技術監督局上班<br />\n<br />\n我的朋友的xx的xx的xx的xx在Xx上班，聽說xxx，消息十分可靠！請廣傳！"},{"pid":"6dbf36edc5f6e34eb22e12a6cbc93d5e7a867c25","tid":944602,"uid":22679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:42:18.000Z","msg":"全部人信回教咪順便唔洗食豬肉囉<br />\n哎呀sor唔記得做回教徒要入集中營添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}